0.10.1 (2012-05-06)

    API Changes:
        - None.

    New Features:
        - None.

    Enhancements:
        - Use Pod::Tidy directly instead of calling out to podtidy(1)
        - Use Perl::Tidy directly instead of calling out to perltidy(1)

    Bug Fixes:
        - None.

0.10.0 (2012-05-06)

    API Changes:
        - None.

    New Features:
        - Support a project-wide ".podtidy-opts" file

    Enhancements:
        - None.

    Bug Fixes:
        - None.

