0.9.1 (2012-05-03)

    API Changes:
        - None.

    New Features:
        - None.

    Enhancements:
        - Second release to CPAN
        - Include dummy App::githook_perltidy module for CPAN indexing
        - Move to a http://semver.org style versioning scheme

    Bug Fixes:
        - _Really_ Handle partially indexed files better on post-commit

